#summary Project Repository

= Introduction =

Need to add this on pom.xml in order to download flex-mojos dependencies


= Details =

`<repositories>
	<repository>
		<id>flex-mojos-repository</id>
		<url>http://flex-mojos.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/repository/</url>
		<releases>
			<enabled>true</enabled>
		</releases>
	</repository>
</repositories>`
